column5: Going to need repoted. I know enough to know its not just a plant its a Tree!
Very close! but the leaves are different. Thankyou though
Good girl... Think good thoughts... & soo Beautifull!
Totally depends on your guy... Get to know what he likes!
Get your health up! Enjoy beeing married & in love. Remind your mother the baby will come when the time is right... Back off... You will have a baby when the time is right. Blessings too you both

Take this into therapy- when the baby was born half your love was taken away from him. He is over compensating & trying to make a happy little family at the same time... Suggestion... Make a regular date night. You both could use it. Am i right?
